= The Bourgeois Fortress

We are currently providing external support to the <span style="color: #4A5C2A;">**Bürgerblock**</span> government of Chancellor [+ chancellor +]. This unprecedented coalition of bourgeois parties - the [? if z_party_name != "CVP": <span style="color: #000000;">**Center**</span>?][? if z_party_name == "CVP": <span style="color: #000000;">**CVP**</span>?], [? if not kvp_formed and dnvp_ideology == "Moderate": <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**DNVP**</span>?][? if kvp_formed: <span style="color: #0087DC;">**KVP**</span>?], [? if not lvp_formed and dvp_exist: <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span>?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**LVP**</span>?], and <span style="color: #DDAA00;">**DDP**</span> - represents a fortress against both the extremes of left and right. But how should we navigate this delicate position?

