@break_toleration
view-if: not constructive_vonc
title: End the toleration agreement with a vote of no confidence!

Are we sure about this? A vote of no confidence would shatter the bourgeois coalition and trigger new elections, potentially leading to massive gains for the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">Nazis</span> and <span style="color: #9B0000;">Communists</span>. [? if in_weimar_coalition_prussia or in_grand_coalition_prussia or in_popular_front_prussia: The <span style="color: #4A5C2A;">Bürgerblock parties</span> also threaten retaliatory action against us in Prussia, pressuring us to maintain stability.?]

- @vonc: Yes, bring down this bourgeois fortress!
- @stay_course: No, we should maintain stability.

